# .nvmrc
# Specifies the Node.js version for this project.
# Used automatically by nvm (Node Version Manager) when you cd into the project.
# See https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm for setup instructions.
#
# This file is populated by the agent based on the active framework's
# Node.js requirements. If building by hand, replace this comment with
# the correct Node.js version number. For example:
#
# 20.11.0
